    "The methodology section highlights that data was primarily sourced from legal professionals, policymakers, and IT specialists engaged in digitization projects.",
    "While this approach captures expert perspectives, it risks overlooking the experiences of endusers, particularly marginalized groups with limited access to digital services.",
    "The exclusion of such voices may inadvertently lead to an overestimation of the success rates of digitization initiatives.Incorporating more diverse participant representation, including public users and grassroots organizations, would provide a more holistic understanding of digitization's impact.",
